                            oc:rowCount 3 ;
                            oc:tableCaption "**Use the `tiny` model for fast transcription** - it's sufficient for most tasks and runs much faster" ;
                            oc:tableMarkdown """| Model | Size | Speed | Accuracy |
|-------|------|-------|----------|
| tiny | 39 MB | Fastest | Good for clear speech |
| base | 74 MB | Fast | Better accuracy |
